data.description: Built in 2021 by Mattamy Homes with upgrades throughout, this Amelia Floor Plan in the Braeburn community is a great place to live in North Carolina. Access to major freeways, shopping, and high rated schools. Corner lot fenced yard w/inground treatment system, stone patio, and front porch view to amenities including pool. Enter your move-in ready home secured by CPI with 6 cameras and security on 1 st floor windows and doors. View this spacious 2850 sqft living area of 4 bedrooms (owner’s deluxe suite on 1st floor and 2nd bedroom suite on 2nd floor), 3-1/2 baths, great room, office, large loft, and 2 car garage. Custom ceiling fans and lighting, additional illuminating lights throughout. Ecobee control system for heating and A/C. Gourmet kitchen w/ large granite island, plenty of cabinets, and walk-in pantry.
